'''2016年拉塔基亞省攻勢'''是敘利亞反政府武裝於2016年6月在[[拉塔基亞省|拉塔基亞省]]發起的一次軍事行動。

==反對派攻佔金薩巴==
2016年6月27日至30日間，由恐怖組織[[努斯拉陣線|努斯拉陣線]]領導的[[征服軍|征服軍]]，在自由敘利亞軍支援下，在拉塔基亞省的{{Link-en|土庫曼山|Turkmen Mountain}}和{{Link-en|庫爾德山|Jabal al-Akrad}}一帶發起攻勢，攻佔數條村莊，後因俄軍空襲而撤退。<ref name="longwarjournal.org"/><ref name="hitandrun">{{cite web|url=https://www.facebook.com/syriahroe/photos/a.150495128392167.28686.121855461256134/893114470796892/?type=3&theater|title=Hit-and-run clashes continue in the... - Syrian Observatory for Human Rights - Facebook|publisher=|accessdate=2 July 2016|archive-date=2019-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190214163437/https://www.facebook.com/syriahroe/photos/a.150495128392167.28686.121855461256134/893114470796892/?type=3&theater|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-recovers-lost-points-northern-latakia-jihadists-retreat-turkey/|title=Syrian Army recovers lost points in northern Latakia as jihadists retreat to Turkey|first=Leith|last=Fadel|date=30 June 2016|publisher=|accessdate=2 July 2016|archive-date=2016-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160816111347/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-recovers-lost-points-northern-latakia-jihadists-retreat-turkey/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-seizes-hilltop-village-near-turkish-border/|title=Syrian Army seizes hilltop village near Turkish border|first=Leith|last=Fadel|date=30 June 2016|publisher=|accessdate=2 July 2016|archive-date=2016-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160816104944/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-seizes-hilltop-village-near-turkish-border/|dead-url=no}}</ref>33名反政府武裝分子及15名政府軍士兵在戰鬥中喪生。<ref name="hitandrun"/>一日後，反對派另一次進攻成功攻佔{{Link-en|金薩巴|Kinsabba}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-mideast-crisis-syria-latakia-idUSKCN0ZH4QA|title=Syria rebels retake key town in western coastal province: monitor, rebels|date=2 July 2016|publisher=|accessdate=2 July 2016|via=Reuters|archive-date=2017-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201131947/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-mideast-crisis-syria-latakia-idUSKCN0ZH4QA|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/rebels-capture-kinsibba-lattakia-province/|title=Rebels capture Kinsibba in Lattakia province|first=Izat|last=Charkatli|date=1 July 2016|publisher=|accessdate=2 July 2016|archive-date=2016-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160816103843/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/rebels-capture-kinsibba-lattakia-province/|dead-url=no}}</ref>及附近多個村莊和小山。作為回應，俄軍在金薩巴和其它數條村莊進行了超過100次空襲。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/russian-air-force-reemerges-northern-latakia-strike-jihadists-near-turkish-border/|title=Russian Air Force reemerges in northern Latakia to strike jihadists near Turkish border|first=Leith|last=Fadel|date=1 July 2016|publisher=|accessdate=2 July 2016|archive-date=2016-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160816163405/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/russian-air-force-reemerges-northern-latakia-strike-jihadists-near-turkish-border/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

7月2日，反對派攻佔土庫曼山區的-{Qal’at}-山山頂。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/jihadists-capture-key-mountaintop-near-turkish-border/|title=Jihadists capture key mountaintop near Turkish border|first=Leith|last=Fadel|date=2 July 2016|publisher=|accessdate=2 July 2016|archive-date=2016-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160816171328/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/jihadists-capture-key-mountaintop-near-turkish-border/|dead-url=no}}</ref>次日，反對派攻佔Saraf村和周圍的小山，後在夜間被政府軍及親政府部隊奪回。<ref name="recaptures" />

==政府軍第一次反攻==
7月8日，敘利亞海軍陸戰隊、沙漠之鷹和特種部隊進攻金薩巴以南的兩處地點，<ref name="massive"/>成功奪回它們。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-gains-ground-latakia-offensive/|title=Syrian Army gains ground in Latakia offensive|first=Izat|last=Charkatli|date=8 July 2016|publisher=|accessdate=9 July 2016|archive-date=2016-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160816174119/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-gains-ground-latakia-offensive/|dead-url=no}}</ref>兩日後，政府軍進攻金薩巴周圍的小山，<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-storms-key-mountaintop-village-northern-latakia/|title=Syrian Army storms key mountaintop village in northern Latakia|first=Leith|last=Fadel|date=10 July 2016|publisher=|accessdate=18 July 2016|archive-date=2016-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160816174116/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-storms-key-mountaintop-village-northern-latakia/|dead-url=no}}</ref>攻佔了數個地點。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-strikes-back-latakia-captures-shilif-castle/|title=Syrian Army strikes back in Latakia as government troops capture Shilif castle|first=Chris|last=Tomson|date=10 July 2016|publisher=|accessdate=18 July 2016|archive-date=2016-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160816145106/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-strikes-back-latakia-captures-shilif-castle/|dead-url=no}}</ref>反對派於同日奪回該些失地。

在7月13日至14日之間的夜間，[[努斯拉陣線|努斯拉陣線]]和[[突厥斯坦伊斯蘭黨|突厥斯坦伊斯蘭黨]]在卡巴尼（Kabbani）地區發起突襲，攻佔了該村以南的Zuwayqat山。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/jihadist-rebels-launch-surprise-offensive-northeast-latakia/|title=Jihadist rebels launch surprise offensive in northeast Latakia|author=Leith Fadel|work=al-Masdar News|date=14 July 2016|accessdate=14 July 2016|archive-date=2016-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160816150924/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/jihadist-rebels-launch-surprise-offensive-northeast-latakia/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

7月16日，政府軍收復金薩巴以南的Qalat Tubal，<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-captures-tubal-castle-northern-latakia/|title=Syrian Army captures Qalat Tubal in northern Latakia|author=Leith Fadel|work=al-Masdar News|date=16 July 2016|accessdate=16 July 2016|archive-date=2016-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160816145358/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-captures-tubal-castle-northern-latakia/|dead-url=no}}</ref>同日稍後更奪回金薩巴。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/syrian-troops-recapture-major-town-coastal-province-40634079|title=Syrian Troops Recapture Major Town in Coastal Province|first=ABC|last=News|publisher=|accessdate=18 July 2016|archive-date=2016-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160717152217/http://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/syrian-troops-recapture-major-town-coastal-province-40634079|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-captures-jihadist-stronghold-latakia-province/|title=Syrian Army captures jihadist stronghold in Latakia province|first=Izat|last=Charkatli|date=16 July 2016|publisher=|accessdate=18 July 2016|archive-date=2016-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160806165553/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-captures-jihadist-stronghold-latakia-province/|dead-url=no}}</ref>連帶周圍的村莊和小山也被政府軍收復。<ref name="recapturesKinsabba">{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-recaptures-kinsabba-latakia-province-map-update/|title=Syrian Army recaptures Kinsabba in Latakia province - Map update|first=Ibra|last=Joudeh|date=16 July 2016|publisher=|accessdate=18 July 2016|archive-date=2016-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160806210720/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-recaptures-kinsabba-latakia-province-map-update/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://edmaps.com/html/latakia_hama_idlib_july_16_201.html|title=Latakia_Hama_Idlib_July_16_2016|publisher=|accessdate=18 July 2016|archive-date=2016-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160825130251/http://www.edmaps.com/html/latakia_hama_idlib_july_16_201.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>次日破曉時，反對派向金薩巴展開反攻，成功奪回該鎮。<ref name="immerses">{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/nothing-battle-immerses-strategic-latakia-town/|title=All-or-nothing battle immerses strategic Latakia town|first=Leith|last=Fadel|date=18 July 2016|publisher=|accessdate=18 July 2016|archive-date=2016-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160806123032/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/nothing-battle-immerses-strategic-latakia-town/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.qasioun.net/en/news/show/31834/Opposition_recapture_Kansaba_and_Shalif_castle_in_north_of_Lattakia|title=Opposition recapture Kansaba and Shalif castle in north of Lattakia - Qasion News Agency|publisher=|accessdate=18 July 2016|archive-date=2016-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160811000639/http://www.qasioun.net/en/news/show/31834/Opposition_recapture_Kansaba_and_Shalif_castle_in_north_of_Lattakia|dead-url=no}}</ref>政府軍於7月18日奪回金薩巴及周圍的村莊和小山。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/video-syrian-army-recaptures-kinsibba-northern-latakia/|title=In Video: Syrian Army recaptures Kinsibba in northern Latakia|first=Zen|last=Adra|date=18 July 2016|publisher=|accessdate=18 July 2016|archive-date=2016-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160806102552/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/video-syrian-army-recaptures-kinsibba-northern-latakia/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-captures-strategic-mountains-northern-latakia-map/|title=Syrian Army captures strategic mountains in northern Latakia: map|first=Leith|last=Fadel|date=18 July 2016|publisher=|accessdate=21 July 2016|archive-date=2016-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160816170353/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-captures-strategic-mountains-northern-latakia-map/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

7月19日，反對派反攻，並動用[[自殺炸彈|自殺炸彈]]客攻擊-{Qal’at Shalaf}-的政府軍據點，逼使政府軍撤退，最終反對派再次攻佔金薩巴。<ref name="suicidebomber">{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/jihadist-suicide-bomber-propels-nusra-key-latakia-town/|title=Jihadist suicide bomber propels Nusra at key Latakia town|first=Leith|last=Fadel|date=19 July 2016|publisher=|accessdate=21 July 2016|archive-date=2016-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160806111601/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/jihadist-suicide-bomber-propels-nusra-key-latakia-town/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.syriahr.com/en/?p=48333 |title=After hours of restoring it… factions and Jabhat Al-Nusra advance again in Kinsabba and Jabal al-Akrad after booby trapped vehicles detonation |accessdate=2016-08-08 |archive-date=2016-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220213748/http://www.syriahr.com/en/?p=48333 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.qasioun.net/en/news/show/32012/Opposition_forces_recapture_Kinsuba_again |title=Opposition forces recapture Kinsuba again |accessdate=2016-08-08 |archive-date=2016-08-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160811001209/http://www.qasioun.net/en/news/show/32012/Opposition_forces_recapture_Kinsuba_again |dead-url=no }}</ref>在金薩巴爭奪戰進行之際，政府軍在該地區收復另外數個村莊。<ref name="advancesin">{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-advances-thei-turkmen-mountains-latakia-map/|title=Syrian Army advances in the Turkmen Mountains of Latakia: map|first=Leith|last=Fadel|date=19 July 2016|publisher=|accessdate=21 July 2016|archive-date=2019-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190203023206/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-advances-thei-turkmen-mountains-latakia-map/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

7月20日，努斯拉陣線在其他反政府軍支援下攻佔Shalaf村，迫使親政府部隊放棄在庫爾德山的新收復據點。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/jihadists-capture-shalaf-village-northern-latakia/|title=Jihadists capture Shalaf village in northern Latakia|first=Leith|last=Fadel|date=21 July 2016|publisher=|accessdate=21 July 2016|archive-date=2019-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190605132204/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/jihadists-capture-shalaf-village-northern-latakia/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

7月28日，[[征服軍|征服軍]]在拉塔基亞省發起新攻勢，旨在攻佔Zuwayqat山區。反對派武裝攻佔該山區後，親政府部隊重新集結和發起反攻，<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/jaysh-al-fateh-captures-mountaintop-northeast-latakia/|title=Jaysh Al-Fateh captures mountaintop in northeast Latakia|first=Leith|last=Fadel|date=28 July 2016|publisher=|accessdate=28 July 2016|archive-date=2016-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160806102626/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/jaysh-al-fateh-captures-mountaintop-northeast-latakia/|dead-url=no}}</ref>成功收復先前的失地。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-recaptures-zuwayqat-mountains-northeast-latakia/|title=Syrian Army recaptures Zuwayqat Mountains in northeast Latakia|first=Leith|last=Fadel|date=28 July 2016|publisher=|accessdate=28 July 2016|archive-date=2016-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160806131904/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-recaptures-zuwayqat-mountains-northeast-latakia/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 第二次政府軍反攻 ==
7月29日，政府軍發起旨在收復金薩巴的新攻勢。政府軍在行動中重新收復Shalaf村，<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-captures-shalaf-village-northern-latakia/|title=Syrian captures Shalaf village in northern Latakia|first=Leith|last=Fadel|date=29 July 2016|publisher=|accessdate=29 July 2016|archive-date=2016-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160816173441/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-captures-shalaf-village-northern-latakia/|dead-url=no}}</ref>卡巴尼村<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.qasioun.net/en/news/show/32953/Fatih_Al_Sham_Front_Seize_Over_Zuwaiqat_Hill_In_Kurd_Mount_Northern_Lattakia_City|title=Fatih Al-Sham Front Seize Over Zuwaiqat Hill In Kurd Mount Northern Lattakia City - Qasion News Agency|publisher=|accessdate=11 August 2016|archive-date=2017-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019185101/http://www.qasioun.net/en/news/show/32953/Fatih_Al_Sham_Front_Seize_Over_Zuwaiqat_Hill_In_Kurd_Mount_Northern_Lattakia_City|dead-url=no}}</ref>及庫爾德山的其它地點也遭到政府軍進攻。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.syriahr.com/en/?p=48878|title=Continued clashes in Lattakia and Der-Ezor|first=|last=|publisher=SOHR|date=29 July 2016|accessdate=29 July 2016|archive-date=2016-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161007213312/http://www.syriahr.com/en/?p=48878|dead-url=no}}</ref>由於政府軍在[[阿勒頗|阿勒頗]]成功[[阿勒頗攻勢_(2016年6月－9月)|包圍]]被反對派控制的東部市區，逼使征服軍從拉塔基亞省抽調兵力到[[阿勒頗|阿勒頗]]協助解圍，導致反對派在拉塔基亞省前線的兵力減弱。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/hundreds-islamist-rebels-leave-latakia-frontline-new-aleppo-offensive/|title=Hundreds of Islamist rebels leave Latakia frontline for new Aleppo offensive|first=Chris|last=Tomson|date=29 July 2016|publisher=|accessdate=30 July 2016|archive-date=2016-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160806135350/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/hundreds-islamist-rebels-leave-latakia-frontline-new-aleppo-offensive/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

7月30日，政府軍從Shalaf直接進攻金薩巴，<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-begins-massive-offensive-northern-latakia/|title=Syrian Army begins massive offensive in northern Latakia|first=Leith|last=Fadel|date=30 July 2016|publisher=|accessdate=30 July 2016|archive-date=2016-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160806121231/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-begins-massive-offensive-northern-latakia/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.syriahr.com/en/?p=48913|title=Continued clashes in Lattakia countryside|publisher=SOHR|date=30 July 2016|accessdate=30 July 2016|archive-date=2016-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220213829/http://www.syriahr.com/en/?p=48913|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.qasioun.net/en/news/show/33056/New_Regime_Offensive_Over_Kensaba_And_Shalaf_Castle_Northern_Lattakia|title=New Regime Offensive Over Kensaba And Shalaf Castle Northern Lattakia|publisher=Qasioun News|date=30 July 2016|accessdate=30 July 2016|archive-date=2016-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160811034814/http://www.qasioun.net/en/news/show/33056/New_Regime_Offensive_Over_Kensaba_And_Shalaf_Castle_Northern_Lattakia|dead-url=no}}</ref>但未能取得進展。<ref name="third">{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-launched-massive-offensive-lattakia-province/|title=Syrian Army launches a massive offensive in Lattakia province|publisher=al-Masdar News|author=Izat Charkatli|date=4 August 2016|accessdate=4 August 2016|archive-date=2016-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160806174225/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-launched-massive-offensive-lattakia-province/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 第三次政府軍反攻 ==
8月4日，親政府部隊再次發起反攻。<ref name="third" />8月6日，親政府部隊成功控制金薩巴周圍的一些據點。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-surrounds-kinsibba-northeast-latakia/|title=Syrian Army surrounds Kinsibba in northeast Latakia|first=Leith|last=Fadel|date=6 August 2016|publisher=|accessdate=6 August 2016|archive-date=2016-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160808161821/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-surrounds-kinsibba-northeast-latakia/|dead-url=no}}</ref>增援金薩巴的反對派武裝遭遇伏擊，16至50人喪生。<ref name="video"/><ref name="encircles">{{Cite web |url=http://www.insidesourcenews.com/#!SAA-Encircles-Rebel-Stronghold-in-Latakia/cjds/57a7a3b80cf28a3dd78321f7 |title=SAA Encircles Rebel Stronghold in Latakia |accessdate=2016-08-08 |archive-date=2016-08-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160830231409/http://www.insidesourcenews.com/#!SAA-Encircles-Rebel-Stronghold-in-Latakia/cjds/57a7a3b80cf28a3dd78321f7 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

在政府軍佔據金薩巴周圍的小山後，反對派撤出金薩巴。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-captures-strategic-latakia-town/|title=Syrian Army captures strategic Latakia town|first=Izat|last=Charkatli|date=2016-08-08|publisher=al-Masdar News|accessdate=2016-08-08|archive-date=2016-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160809212411/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-captures-strategic-latakia-town/|dead-url=no}}</ref>8月8日政府軍進入金薩巴，但是不久就遭到反對派的快速反擊而被逼撤出，政府軍在獲得增援後再度收復金薩巴及周圍地區。<ref name="breaking">{{cite web|url=http://www.insidesourcenews.com/#!BREAKING-SAA-Captures-Strategic-Kinsibba/cjds/57a83c290cf2fdb0f74c8e3f|title=The Inside Source|publisher=|accessdate=11 August 2016|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160830231409/http://www.insidesourcenews.com/#!BREAKING-SAA-Captures-Strategic-Kinsibba/cjds/57a83c290cf2fdb0f74c8e3f|archivedate=2016年8月30日}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.syriahr.com/2016/08/08/%D9%82%D9%88%D8%A7%D8%AA-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%86%D8%B8%D8%A7%D9%85-%D8%AA%D8%B3%D8%AA%D8%B9%D9%8A%D8%AF-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B3%D9%8A%D8%B7%D8%B1%D8%A9-%D8%B9%D9%84%D9%89-%D9%85%D9%86%D8%B7%D9%82%D8%A9-%D9%83/ |title=قوات النظام تستعيد السيطرة على منطقة كنسبا ومحيطها بجبل الأكراد |accessdate=2018-02-25 |archive-date=2018-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180226121430/http://www.syriahr.com/2016/08/08/%D9%82%D9%88%D8%A7%D8%AA-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%86%D8%B8%D8%A7%D9%85-%D8%AA%D8%B3%D8%AA%D8%B9%D9%8A%D8%AF-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B3%D9%8A%D8%B7%D8%B1%D8%A9-%D8%B9%D9%84%D9%89-%D9%85%D9%86%D8%B7%D9%82%D8%A9-%D9%83/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>先前被反對派攻佔的其它村莊也幾乎全數被政府軍陸續收復。<ref name="50militants">{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/50-militants-killed-latakia-battles-today-map-update/|title=More than 50 militants were killed in Latakia battles today (Map Update)|first=Izat|last=Charkatli|date=8 August 2016|publisher=|accessdate=11 August 2016|archive-date=2018-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180226132939/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/50-militants-killed-latakia-battles-today-map-update/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-makes-major-advances-latakia-videomap/|title=Syrian Army makes major advances in Latakia (Video+Map)|first=Izat|last=Charkatli|date=8 August 2016|publisher=|accessdate=11 August 2016|archive-date=2018-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180226045849/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-makes-major-advances-latakia-videomap/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.syriahr.com/2016/08/09/%D9%82%D8%B5%D9%81-%D9%84%D9%82%D9%88%D8%A7%D8%AA-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%86%D8%B8%D8%A7%D9%85-%D9%8A%D8%B1%D8%A7%D9%81%D9%82-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A7%D8%B4%D8%AA%D8%A8%D8%A7%D9%83%D8%A7%D8%AA-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%85-2/ |title=قصف لقوات النظام يرافق الاشتباكات المتواصلة بجبال اللاذقية |accessdate=2018-02-25 |archive-date=2016-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160809191330/http://www.syriahr.com/2016/08/09/%D9%82%D8%B5%D9%81-%D9%84%D9%82%D9%88%D8%A7%D8%AA-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%86%D8%B8%D8%A7%D9%85-%D9%8A%D8%B1%D8%A7%D9%81%D9%82-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A7%D8%B4%D8%AA%D8%A8%D8%A7%D9%83%D8%A7%D8%AA-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%85-2/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

